<br>
Creapiing slowly came up to Kelranon's gate, and pressed a button that seemed to be a doorbell. She tried to look through the gate, but was startled when she saw a rotting corpse looking right back at her. In a whispering, scratchy voice, he spoke, &quot;What do you want?&quot; Creapiing shook her head and replied, &quot;I need to speak with Kelranon about...well that is none of your business, let me through.&quot;<br>
<br>
The zombie trooper, not too sure as to what to do, opened the gate for her. The other troopers all inspected her and examined her and made sure she wasn't here to assasinate their master.<br>
<br>
Creapiing stepped up to the large, eerie mansion. She got closer, and she was again startled, but this time by the dogs there. She heard them barking and turned around to see two great danes tied up to a post by magic chains, jumping and barking at Creapiing. She let out a sigh and entered the house. She got no more than 3 steps in when she heard,<br>
&quot;What do you want?&quot; <br>
